      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Leave No Trace Behind",
        "Client": "World-Renowned Martial Artist",
        "Description": "I teach the art of fighting an\r\ninvisible opponent. Remain\r\ncalm, for your enemy will\r\ngive away their position. I\u0027m\r\ntrained to fight humans, not\r\nbeasts, so I shall leave the\r\nmonster to you.",
        "Target": "Slay a Chameleos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Passage invisible",
        "Client": "Ma\u00EEtre mondial du karat\u00E9",
        "Description": "J\u0027enseigne l\u0027art consistant \u00E0\r\naffronter un adversaire invisible.\r\nIl faut rester calme pour\r\nd\u00E9couvrir l\u0027endroit o\u00F9 se trouve\r\nl\u0027ennemi. J\u0027affronte uniquement\r\nles humains, donc je te\r\nlaisse les monstres.",
        "Target": "Tuer un Chameleos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Senza traccia",
        "Client": "Artista marziale famoso",
        "Description": "Insegno l\u0027arte di combattere\r\ncontro avversari invisibili.\r\nMantieni la calma e il nemico\r\nsveler\u00E0 la sua posizione. Sono\r\naddestrato per lottare contro\r\nessere umani, non bestie,\r\nquindi ai mostri pensaci tu.",
        "Target": "Uccidi un Chameleos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Keine Spur hinterlassen",
        "Client": "Ber\u00FChmter Kampfk\u00FCnstler",
        "Description": "Ich lehre die Kunst des Kampfes\r\ngegen einen unsichtbaren Geg-\r\nner. Bleibe ruhig, dann verr\u00E4t\r\nder Gegner, wo er ist. Ich bin\r\nim Kampf gegen Menschen\r\ntrainiert, nicht Bestien, daher\r\n\u00FCberlasse ich die Monster dir.",
        "Target": "Erlege einen Chameleos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Sin dejar rastro",
        "Client": "Archifamoso artista marcial",
        "Description": "Yo ense\u00F1o el arte de combatir\r\na un oponente invisible.\r\nMant\u00E9n la calma, y tu enemigo\r\nrevelar\u00E1 su posici\u00F3n.\r\nTengo formaci\u00F3n para luchar\r\ncontra humanos, no bestias;\r\nas\u00ED que el monstruo, para ti.",
        "Target": "Abate un Chameleos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
